main event: Two round white objects the size of a quarter were observed in the sky over Dallas, Texas.
interesting points: The objects were seen at a 30 degree elevation for a total of 8 minutes., The objects split and disappeared into the horizon., The sighting lasted for 7 minutes before the objects vanished., The report concludes that there is insufficient data for evaluation., There were no photographs included in the report.
witness description: an electrical engineer and a housewife
